children.description: Given Navigate to MIS Beta Application
Launch MIS beta
And Login to MIS with credentials "amisha.srivastava" "Gemini@123"
Login to MIS: amisha.srivastava, Gemini@123
Then Open "Manage Task Template" page of "TimeSheet" module
Navigate to page: Manage Task Template, TimeSheet
And Verify "Manage Task Template" page of type "Sub"
Verify page: Manage Task Template, Sub
And Add a new valid task template with "Lmno" "njuik" "Gemini" "Reporting"
Click delete template: Lmno
Verify and accept confirmation
Click add new template
Add valid template: Lmno, njuik, Gemini, Reporting
And Edit a task template "Lmno" with "wxyz" "MyTemplate" "FES" "Testing"
